                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for John Hammond &amp;lt;john.hammond@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/d32f5122-318c-11e3-905d-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/d32f5122-318c-11e3-905d-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_52 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;tar: /mnt/lustre/d0.conf-sanity/d52/f.conf-sanity.52-7: file changed as we read it&lt;br/&gt;
Unable to tar files&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: conf-sanity 52&lt;/p&gt;</description>
